           paste0("Coron, L., Delaigue, O., Thirel, G., Dorchies, D., Perrin, C. and Michel, C. (",
                  year,
                  "). airGR: Suite of GR Hydrological Models for Precipitation-Runoff Modelling. ",
                  note, ", ",
